<item>
            <title>[LU-5946] jobstats are not expired if no new jobs arrive</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5946</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The jobstats data is not expired for a device if new jobids are not arriving at the server.  This means that the stats may stick around far longer than necessary.  They should be expired when they get too old.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
